Bookmark is a mobile app that allows book lovers to buy/rent books from people near them.

Bookmark is built on ionic platform making it a hybrid web app. It is currently supported on android and ios.

The app has 4 main pages :
* chat
* book list
* book search
* profile

Data storage 
Firebase : data is accessed directly from the client-end point by the app instead of using an external server

There are 4 main services used in Bookmark : 
* Search - to find a book in Google, Amazon and Goodreads book library
* location - provide geographical services like determining address, distance between points
* currency - provides the currency of any country